description:

Experience the rich flavors of Rajasthan with our authentic Rajasthani Mangodi, a culinary delight. Recommend Use:
Mangodi ki Daal
  • Heat ghee in a pressure cooker and add cumin seeds and asafoetida. Sauté until the seeds crackle.

  • Stir in the chopped tomatoes, ginger-green chilli paste, turmeric powder, chilli powder, coriander powder, and salt. Mix well.
  • Pour in 2½ cups of water, close the pressure cooker, and cook for 2 whistles.
  • Add 1½ cups of water and lemon juice, and simmer for 1 to 2 minutes while stirring occasionally.
  • Serve Mangodi ki Dal hot, garnished with fresh coriander.
